        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孔融无谋将我荐"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "催马来在长亭看"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荀彧"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荀攸智谋浅"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "必是与我把行饯"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等不得远迎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺日前进府，与曹操深施一礼，他昂然不动。今日长亭，连他众谋士也是这等"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大模大样。他们轻慢于我，但取笑一番。他有来言，我有去语。吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四海相逢初见面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人生须得礼为先。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问我一声回一言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长亭假装把泪展"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡见了我等，为何啼哭？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是祢衡泪不干，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我今有言听心间："
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁知来在灵棺前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "指望来在古阳关"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大狂徒。我等死尸，你乃无头狂鬼。尚不知耻！"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺本大丈夫，汉朝之臣，不做曹操之党。某怎得无头？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺丞相福大量大，不与你计较。荆州刘表，性如烈火。你若出言不逊，将你一"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刀分为两段，岂不是无头狂鬼？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺祢衡宁做他乡之鬼，不做贼佞之臣！岂你等趋炎附势，只图眼前富贵，那知"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臭名万载。无耻之辈，不足与吾谈论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你乃无耻之辈。胸中有什么策议，出此狂言？"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要问我胸中策论，展开你们驴耳，听俺道来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你道俺胸中无策论，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "战国、春秋日夜精。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下能安邦保黎民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可比韩信赛陈平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要把贼子一笔倾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上能治国如尧舜"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "安排摆兵和布阵"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有日大展经纶手"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大狂徒乱舌根，"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自负才高夸己能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相之命敢不遵？"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好去他乡做鬼魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三军满斟葡萄酒"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今领吾一杯酒"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用手接过酒一樽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将杯不饮奠埃尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先奠荀彧死尸灵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是祢衡酒不饮"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀攸",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手捧葡萄酒一樽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀攸",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与祢衡来饯行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀攸",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿此去早归阴！"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀攸",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今饮吾一杯酒"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荀攸须为汉朝臣，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今做曹操帐下宾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫你千年万载落骂名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将酒奠在尘埃地"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "阳关饯行酒一樽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一腔恶气往上喷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂肯敬酒与狂生？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程昱",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若不奉了丞相命"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣报君恩子奉亲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你本不忠不孝人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天雷霹死儿当身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将酒奠在尘埃地"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭嘉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郭嘉奉酒泪淋淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭嘉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手捧葡萄吊亡魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭嘉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿早死早脱身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "郭嘉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你今饮干吾的酒"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "郭嘉不必两泪淋，"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "短命年少小姣生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿是披麻戴孝人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有事关心少留停。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还有一事少叮咛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子狗党仔细听："
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亦非凡间等闲人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将俺谪贬下凡尘；"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀却朝中狗谗臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等回复曹奸佞："
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宽心稳坐听信音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祢衡当朝做公卿；"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却是孝子与贤孙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "祢衡",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "跨马扬鞭走一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（祢衡笑，下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长亭去了祢正平，"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去时有路回无门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位先生，祢衡言语狂妄，荆州吉凶难料。你我回复丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "左右，带马回府交令去者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
